init_text: Your entire life, you've been told you're deathly allergic to bees. You've always had people protecting you from them, be it your mother or a hired hand. Today, one slips through and lands on your shoulder. You hear a tiny voice say "Your Majesty, what are your orders?"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The second thing you notice is that you have a lot of bees around you, all of them bowing.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You're not sure how you feel about this.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The teller looks at you funny, and you realize that you're covered in bees.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You realize that the bees have stung everyone in the bank, and you're the only one left.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You grab some cash and run.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You're not sure what to do with all this money.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You decide to buy a new car.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The salesman looks at you funny, and you realize that you're covered in bees.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You decide to go to the mall.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You also have a lot of bees.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You head back to your new house, and the bees follow.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You get in bed, and the bees get in bed with you.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You fall asleep, and they fall asleep.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The next morning, you wake up to find that you have been stung to death.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The room is empty and silent.

actions.name: text-delete
actions.text: The room is empty and silent.

actions.name: text-delete
actions.text: You fall back asleep for the last time.
